Author: sipapito
Text: I like to lay on my back and put my legs up on the wall or just hold them up for a bit and then get up and walk around. It gets the blood circulating more and usually eases pain a bit. Or a warm Epsom salt bath if you're able!!

Author: DoggyDish
Text: Sounds like an electrolyte imbalance. Try getting some potassium and increasing your liquids!
